fade_in_bottom_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

fade_out_bottom_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

fade_out_down(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

fade_out_left(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

fade_out_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

fade_out_top_left(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

fade_out_top_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

fade_out_up(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

fade_out(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

roll_in_left(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

roll_in_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

roll_out_left(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

roll_out_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

shake_vertical(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

shake_horizontal(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

blur_in(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

blur_out(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

slide_in_down(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

slide_in_left(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

slide_in_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

slide_in_up(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

slide_out_down(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

slide_out_left(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

slide_out_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

throb(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

swivel_vertical(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

swivel_vertical_double(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

wheel_in_left(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

wheel_in_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

wheel_out_left(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

wheel_out_right(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

flash(ui, duration = NULL, delay = NULL)

Arguments

ui

A UI element
duration

Duration of animation; Enter word: "fast" = 800 milliseconds, "faster" = 500 milliseconds, "fastest" = 300 milliseconds, "slow" = 2 seconds, "slower" = 3 seconds, "slowest" = 4 seconds
delay

Delay in seconds before animation starts; Enter value: 0 - 5

Examples

if (interactive()) {
  library(shiny)
  library(vov)

  ui <- fluidPage(
    use_vov(),
    fade_in_bottom_left(
      h1("Hello world!")
    )
  )

  server <- function(input, output, session) {}

  shinyApp(ui, server)
}
